Class ProtocolData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hawq.pxf.api.utilities.InputData
      • org.apache.hawq.pxf.service.utilities.ProtocolData

  • public class ProtocolData
extends InputData
    Common configuration of all MetaData classes. Provides read-only access to common parameters supplied using system properties.

        public int getStatsMaxFragments()

        Returns:

      • getStatsSampleRatio

        public float getStatsSampleRatio()
        Statistics parameter. Returns a number between 0.0001 and 1.0, representing the sampling ratio on each fragment for ANALYZE sampling. The value is set in HAWQ side based on ANALYZE computations and the number of sampled fragments.
        Returns:
        sampling ratio
